{"readme":"<h1 class=\"title\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://github.com/dmnsgn/primitive-geometry\">primitive-geometry </a><div class=\"contrib\"></div></h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://travis-ci.org/dmnsgn/primitive-geometry\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/primitive-geometry\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier\"></a></p>\n<p>A package exporting geometries for 3D rendering, including normals, UVs and cell indices (faces). Perfect if you want to supercharge your <code>node_modules</code> folder... with 100KB of geometries.</p>\n<p><iframe scrolling=\"no\" seamless=\"seamless\" src=\"https://dmnsgn.github.io/primitive-geometry/\"></iframe></p>\n<p>See the <a href=\"https://dmnsgn.github.io/primitive-geometry/\">demo</a> and its <a href=\"http://github.com/dmnsgn/primitive-geometry/blob/master/demo/index.js\">source</a> for an example with <a href=\"http://regl.party/\">REGL</a>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"installation\">Installation</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"lang-bash\"><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source shell\"><span>npm&#xA0;install&#xA0;primitive-geometry</span></span></div>\n</code></pre>\n<p><a href=\"https://nodei.co/npm/primitive-geometry/\"></a></p>\n<h2 id=\"usage\">Usage</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"lang-js\"><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>const&#xA0;Primitives&#xA0;=&#xA0;require(&quot;primitive-geometry&quot;);</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>&#xA0;</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>const&#xA0;quadGeometry&#xA0;=&#xA0;Primitives.quad();</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>const&#xA0;planeGeometry&#xA0;=&#xA0;Primitives.plane();</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>const&#xA0;cubeGeometry&#xA0;=&#xA0;Primitives.cube();</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>const&#xA0;roundedCubeGeometry&#xA0;=&#xA0;Primitives.roundedCube();</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>const&#xA0;capsuleGeometry&#xA0;=&#xA0;Primitives.capsule();</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>const&#xA0;sphereGeometry&#xA0;=&#xA0;Primitives.sphere();</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>const&#xA0;icosphereGeometry&#xA0;=&#xA0;Primitives.icosphere();</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>const&#xA0;ellipsoidGeometry&#xA0;=&#xA0;Primitives.ellipsoid();</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>const&#xA0;torusGeometry&#xA0;=&#xA0;Primitives.torus();</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>const&#xA0;cylinderGeometry&#xA0;=&#xA0;Primitives.cylinder();</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>//&#xA0;without&#xA0;normals/uvs</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>const&#xA0;boxGeometry&#xA0;=&#xA0;Primitives.box();</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>const&#xA0;circleGeometry&#xA0;=&#xA0;Primitives.circle();</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>&#xA0;</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>console.log(quadGeometry);</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>//&#xA0;{</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>//&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0;positions:&#xA0;[&#xA0;[x,&#xA0;y,&#xA0;z],&#xA0;[x,&#xA0;y,&#xA0;z],&#xA0;...&#xA0;],</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>//&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0;cells:&#xA0;[&#xA0;[a,&#xA0;b,&#xA0;c],&#xA0;[a,&#xA0;b,&#xA0;c],&#xA0;...&#xA0;],</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>//&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0;uvs:&#xA0;[&#xA0;[u,&#xA0;v],&#xA0;[u,&#xA0;v],&#xA0;...&#xA0;],</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>//&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0;normals:&#xA0;[&#xA0;[x,&#xA0;y,&#xA0;z],&#xA0;[x,&#xA0;y,&#xA0;z],&#xA0;...&#xA0;]</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>//&#xA0;}</span></span></div>\n</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"api\">API</h2>\n<p>See individual packages for details:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://npmjs.com/package/primitive-quad\">primitive-quad</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://npmjs.com/package/primitive-plane\">primitive-plane</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://npmjs.com/package/primitive-cube\">primitive-cube</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://npmjs.com/package/primitive-rounded-cube\">primitive-rounded-cube</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://npmjs.com/package/primitive-capsule\">primitive-capsule</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://npmjs.com/package/primitive-sphere\">primitive-sphere</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://npmjs.com/package/primitive-icosphere\">primitive-icosphere</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://npmjs.com/package/primitive-ellipsoid\">primitive-ellipsoid</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://npmjs.com/package/primitive-torus\">primitive-torus</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://npmjs.com/package/primitive-cylinder\">primitive-cylinder</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://npmjs.com/package/primitive-box\">primitive-box</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://npmjs.com/package/primitive-circle\">primitive-circle</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"license\">License</h2>\n<p>MIT. See <a href=\"https://github.com/dmnsgn/primitive-geometry/blob/master/LICENSE.md\">license file</a>.</p>\n"}